sequenceDiagram
    participant ServiceA as Client Service
    participant AuthServer as Authorization Server
    participant ServiceB as Resource Server

    ServiceA->>AuthServer: POST /token with client_id + client_secret + scope
    AuthServer-->>AuthServer: Validate credentials and scope
    alt Credentials valid
        AuthServer-->>ServiceA: Access token (JWT, short-lived)
    else Credentials invalid
        AuthServer-->>ServiceA: 401 Unauthorized
    end
    ServiceA->>ServiceB: GET /api/data with Bearer token
    ServiceB-->>ServiceB: Validate token signature and scope
    alt Token valid
        ServiceB-->>ServiceA: 200 OK with resource data
    else Token expired or invalid
        ServiceB-->>ServiceA: 401 Unauthorized
        ServiceA->>AuthServer: POST /token (re-authenticate)
        AuthServer-->>ServiceA: New access token
        ServiceA->>ServiceB: Retry request with new token
        ServiceB-->>ServiceA: 200 OK with resource data
    end
